{"tid":1251874,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"一個人三哥食70蚊會唔會太貴","createTime":"2019-06-22T17:15:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T23:02:38.000Z","uid":157735,"like":16,"dislike":99,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"634b18769ece53872f591e001c77ee82ac66502e","tid":1251874,"uid":157735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T17:15:56.000Z","msg":"成日一個毒拎食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上曬癮咁 因為本身自己好中意麻辣<br />\n三哥又可以多麻 然後一般肚餓三個送 唔肚餓一個送又太寡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 起碼兩個<br />\n因為食開中辣 又要加野飲<br />\n之後中意叫雞翼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一個人食三隻 （五隻都完全食得曬）<br />\n70-80買單<br />\n最近仲嚴重左成日食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我係咪已中三哥毒<br />\n（相反譚仔食得多係會唔想食）"},{"pid":"54e3a187672e96fed4722b430b6e2dc354590291","tid":1251874,"uid":62822,"like":58,"dislike":1,"score":57,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T17:16:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5aa007294dba225f96d30328816802b9cc41f52d","tid":1251874,"uid":227275,"like":124,"dislike":2,"score":122,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T17:19:20.000Z","msg":"譚仔3餸好撚笨柒  <br />\n1餸同3餸份量都一樣 3餸會分薄曬<br />\n1餸再叫一個小食 再叫野飲最fit"},{"pid":"fd5ba0f6a42ec5ddd88b0d33387763d7ed13b76d","tid":1251874,"uid":157735,"like":1,"dislike":17,"score":-16,"quote":{"pid":"5aa007294dba225f96d30328816802b9cc41f52d","tid":1251874,"uid":227275,"like":124,"dislike":2,"score":122,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T17:19:20.000Z","msg":"譚仔3餸好撚笨柒  <br />\n1餸同3餸份量都一樣 3餸會分薄曬<br />\n1餸再叫一個小食 再叫野飲最fit"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T17:25:04.000Z","msg":"我試過叫牛肉韭菜<br />\n你要知平時韭菜本身多 但一來係<strong>全碗</strong><br />\n我以為咩事 食食下先知佢冇落牛肉<br />\n所以按照一個送送多的principle我碗野就變左韭菜湯底 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2bd218752438ffa1f77a4336adfc43ac67596f0","tid":1251874,"uid":104900,"like":42,"dislike":12,"score":30,"quote":{"pid":"5aa007294dba225f96